===Etymology===
Common Germanic ''*sturkaz'', from Proto-Indo-European ''*str̥gos'', probably an extension of ''*ster-'' "stiff" (from its movements). Near cognates include Old Norse ''[[storkr]]'' and Old High German ''[[storh]]''
